title: Deep-diving robotic sub could be last hope for lost Titanic tourists
description: With only hours left to save those aboard the lost Titanic submersible, a French underwater robot called Victor 6000 could be the rescue effort’s last hope.

title: AI-powered commentary is coming to next month’s Wimbledon
description: Sports commentators who thought they were safe from the ever-expanding tentacles of generative AI should think again.
